Robert P. Maida 
Executive Compensation
As Vice President of Operational Excellence at ALLIED MOTION TECHNOLOGIES, Robert P. Maida  made $375,364 in total compensation.  Of this total $210,250 was received as a salary, $57,459 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $91,103 was awarded as stock and $16,552 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


